      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "It took a _lot_ of debugging cryptic errors with the help of @dongcarl to figure out that the error I was running into was to due to trying to build guix on a physical SSD drive. It's also just faster to use a RAM drive.\r\n\r\nI suppose I could try building guix from scratch without this to see if it's still an issue.",
